DTEND;TZID=Asia/Kolkata:20260602T000000
SUMMARY:🌙 6-HOUR SIMULATION #1
DESCRIPTION:Full exam simulation. Block 6 PM to midnight. Select 5-6 challenges from PicoCTF and your PYQ recreations. Strict timer, no phone, no distractions. Mimic real exam conditions exactly.\n\nCategories to include: 2 Web, 1 Crypto, 1 Forensics, 1 OSINT, 1 Misc.
